ets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 草十年被人一Q 清袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec196269ffa95ce4adba040e8ac88777a6470a52","tid":901993,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14295e886920d03235cc1953d7d1bca5a9cab31f","tid":901993,"uid":40845,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T13:10:38.000Z","msg":"剝實剝到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係好既牙醫會剝之前會建議你植牙，因為如果你無端端冇咗隻牙，其他牙齒就會好容易移位，到最後就係全部甩曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前我隻臼齒蛀到得番條邊邊，一心諗住剝咗佢，個老牙醫同我講咗半個鐘話咁後生剝牙係唔好，結果用咗六千幾補牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T13:39:36.000Z","msg":"移位到最後全部甩晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩黃綠醫生嚟"},{"pid":"ad0fa01e789eb52bab846c2b87be3531cff5461d","tid":901993,"uid":22632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T13:41:05.000Z","msg":"我早排都整左五千幾<br />\n黎緊整埋牙套又多幾千<br />\n早晚刷牙 牙線 漱口水<br />\n一年睇一次牙醫全部做哂<br />\n咪唔洗在煩囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲嘢唔懶得"},{"pid":"b8bd6e1ca785e2f520f5c8c12521cd8119577de8","tid":901993,"uid":22632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ee47b84a03fef36fce39ae81be3b22c9e8e35da","tid":901993,"uid":194630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c22e714a34192f43565bf2f78a7b0f143b0e8af3","tid":901993,"uid":40845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f5b69ab9c1423f43560723c6266c519d657bbf7","tid":901993,"uid":194630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T13:28:32.000Z","msg":"唔撚係掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkg